      <h1 align="center">December 13, 2010 Best Buy Gift Card Sweepstakes Official Rules</h1>
      <p align="center"> NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. A PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND WILL NOT INCREASE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING.   	THIS PROMOTION IS NOT AFFILIATED WITH OR ADMINISTERED BY FACEBOOK IN ANY WAY. </p>
      <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
      <p>The December 13, 2010 Best Buy Gift Card Sweepstakes (the   &quot;Promotion&quot;) is administered by Big Prize Giveaways, LLC (&quot;BPG&quot;) and is   open to residents age 18 and older in all jurisdictions where receipt of   prizes or entry in the Promotion is not prohibited by United States   and/or local laws, rules or regulations. Prohibited countries include,   but are not limited to, Belgium, Norway, Sweden, India and residents of   any country embargoed by the United States.  Employees of BPG or any of   its respective affiliates, subsidiaries, advertising agencies,   participating sponsor or any other company involved with the design,   production, execution or distribution of the Promotion and their   immediate family (spouse, parents, siblings and children) and household   members of each such employees are not eligible. The Promotion is   subject to all applicable federal, state and local laws and regulations.   Void where prohibited. Participation constitutes entrant's (and   entrant's parent/legal guardian, if entrant is a Minor) full and   unconditional agreement to these Official Rules and BPG's decisions,   which are final and binding in all matters related to the Promotion.   Winning a prize is contingent upon fulfilling all requirements set forth   herein. The Promotion consists of a sweepstakes (the &quot;Sweepstakes&quot;).</p>
      <h2>2. Administrator</h2>
      <p>Big Prize Giveaways, LLC (PO Box 5963, Columbia, SC 29205) is the sole Administrator of the Sweepstakes.</p>
      <h2>3. Timing</h2>
      <p>The Promotion begins on December 8, 2010 at 12:00 PM Eastern Time   (&quot;ET&quot;) and ends on December 13, 2010 at 5:00 PM ET (the &quot;Promotion   Period&quot;). Administrator's computer is the official time keeping device   for this Promotion.</p>
      <h2>4. How to Enter</h2>
      <p>There are two (2) ways to enter: </p>
      <ol>
        <li>Personal Entry: You can enter the Promotion through the Big Prize   application on the Facebook Platform using the following address: <a href="http://www.bigprize.com/share/bestbuy">http://www.bigprize.com/share/bestbuy</a>.    Follow the on-screen prompts to enter. This will give you one entry   and a friend of your choice (optional) one entry. You may only submit   one Personal entry per day.</li>
        <li>Friend Entry: When one of your friends submits a Personal Entry and   lists your name as the friend of their choice, (as noted in number 1   above) that friend will receive one Personal Entry and you will receive   one Friend Entry. There is no limit to the number of valid Friend   Entries you may receive per day from this method.</li>
      </ol>
      <strong><em>General Conditions Regarding Entering:</em></strong> Entry requires   using the Big Prize application and you must become a fan of Big Prize   Giveaways' Page on Facebook to access features of the Big Prize   Giveaways Application. Use of any automated system to participate is   prohibited and may result in disqualification. Sponsor is not   responsible for lost, late, incomplete, invalid, unintelligible or   misdirected registrations, which will be disqualified. Potential winners   may be required to show proof of identity.  In the event of a dispute   as to the identity of the rightful winner, Big Prize will gather proof   of identity from the disputing parties and will solely be responsible   for choosing the winner. There is no charge for entering as free   Internet access is available at many public libraries. <strong>This   promotion is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or   associated with, Facebook. You are providing your information to Big   Prize Giveaways and not to Facebook.</strong> The information you provide will only be used to administer the promotion and in accordance with our privacy policy.
      <h2>5. Winner Selection</h2>
      <p>BPG will conduct a drawing at 5:00 pm on December 13, 2010 by   randomly selecting one Personal Entry from all Personal Entries properly   submitted during the Promotion Period. The entrant who submitted the   selected Personal Entry along with entrant listed on the corresponding   Friend Entry, if applicable, will be Potential Grand Prize Winners.</p>
      <h2>6. Verification and Notification of Potential Grand Prize Winner</h2>
      <p>ALL POTENTIAL SWEEPSTAKES WINNERS ARE SUBJECT TO VERIFICATION BY BPG   WHOSE DECISIONS ARE FINAL AND BINDING IN ALL MATTERS RELATED TO THE   PROMOTION. Potential Grand Prize Winners must continue to comply with   all terms and conditions of these Official Rules, and winning is   contingent upon fulfilling all requirements. Potential Grand Prize   Winners will be posted on the following web page: <a href="http://www.bigprize.com/winners_list">http://www.bigprize.com/winners_list</a>.   The potential winners must respond within 7 days of his/her name being   posted. In addition and as a courtesy, BPG will also attempt to alert   the Potential Grand Prize Winners using the email address provided   during the entry process, but BPG is not responsible for any technical   malfunction or undelivered email messages. IT IS YOUR RESPONSIBILITY TO   CHECK THE WEBSITE ADDRESS ABOVE AFTER THE CONCLUSION OF THIS PROMOTION   TO SEE IF YOU ARE A POTENTIAL GRAND PRIZE WINNER. Once the potential   winners have been verified to the satisfaction of BPG, BPG will arrange   for prize fulfillment. If the selected potential Grand Prize Winners are   determined to be ineligible by BPG, or fail to respond within the   required time period, the potential winners forfeit their prizes and are   disqualified. Otherwise, the selected potential Grand Prize Winners   become the Validated Grand Prize Winners. In the event that potential   Grand Prize Winners of a prize are disqualified for any reason, BPG may   in BPG’s sole discretion randomly select different winners from all   remaining eligible entries and repeat the verification process outlined   above, donate the forfeited prizes to charity or conduct a new promotion   to award the prizes.</p>
      <h2>7. Prizes</h2>
      <p>A maximum of two &quot;Grand Prizes&quot; each consisting of a $100 Best Buy   Gift Card ($100) may be awarded. Winners are responsible for all taxes   and fees associated with prize receipt and/or use. Total actual retail   value of all prizes will not exceed $200. </p>
      <h2>8. Odds of Winning</h2>
      <p>The odds of winning will depend on the number of entries. Many will enter, few will win.</p>
