      <p>Except where prohibited, participation in the Promotion constitutes   winners consent to Sponsor's and its agents' use of winner's name,   likeness, photograph, voice, opinions, hometown and state, and/or   uploaded photo or slide show for promotional purposes in any media,   worldwide, without further payment or consideration.</p>
